title: Looking To Trade T206 For 1933 Goudey
author: MacDice

posts.post_title: Looking To Trade T206 For 1933 Goudey
posts.post_content: I have finally decided to admit that the monster has defeated me.  I have around 50-60 low grad raw commons all in individual screw downs that I am looking to trade for raw 1933 Goudeys (especially Earl Averill cards).  Please send me a PM if anyone is interested in trading.

Here is what I still have available for trade.  Would consider selling if someone was looking for lots of 10 or more.  Too busy to scan one and two cards at a time...its hockey season and fall ball has begun for baseball.
